query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS trades (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  messageId VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  team1 VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL,
  team2 VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL,
  team1Players TEXT NOT NULL,
  team2Players TEXT NOT NULL,
  status ENUM('pending', 'approved', 'rejected', 'reversed') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'pending',
  upvotes INT NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  downvotes INT NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  approvedBy VARCHAR(255),
  rejectedBy VARCHAR(255),
  reversedBy VARCHAR(255),
  createdAt TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  processedAt TIMESTAMP NULL,
  reversedAt TIMESTAMP NULL
)
